title: Bostitch Office QuietSharp Executive Heavy Duty Electric Pencil Sharpener, Colored-Pencil Compatible, Black
description: Ideal for home, home office or work area. Heavy-duty electric pencil sharpener features hardened steel cutting blades to ensure a good point every time. Easy-to-remove shaving tray. Built-in safety guard prohibits operation when shavings tray is removed. Auto-stop feature prevents oversharpening.
